      "text": "gotten after [REDACTED] who is slowly disintegrating.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "[REDACTED] stated she does not have this letter.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "[REDACTED] became hysterical on the phone, and stated that",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
